 SG_ VCU_DutyCycle m32 : 24|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] "%"  MD_Range
 SG_ VCU_Frequency m32 : 16|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] "Hz"  MD_Range
 SG_ VCU_Direction m32 : 8|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MD_Range
 SG_ VCU_RequestByte M : 0|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MD_Range

