CM_ SG_ 2565829248 VCU_CurrentLimit "the maximum average continueous current (2 seconds), range 0.1A to 25A and all other values will set the current limit to default 25A";
CM_ SG_ 2565829248 VCU_Timeout "range 0.1s to 25s, all other value make it to default 7 seconds";
CM_ SG_ 2565829248 VCU_DutyCycle "range 0 to 100%, all other value make duty cycle 50%";
CM_ SG_ 2565829248 VCU_Frequency "range 2Hz to 250Hz, all other values make frequency 0Hz";
